Sallies Unit to Re-Open Witkop Mine; Cooke Named as Acting Chief Executive

-- B y   V e r n o n   W e s s e l s
-- 
2011-02-15T07:01:34Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-15/sallies-unit-to-re-open-witkop-mine-cooke-named-as-acting-chief-executive.html
  Sallies Ltd . said its Witkop
Fluorspar Mine Ltd. unit will be re-opening its Witkop Mine
after negotiations with its key customers secured sizeable
orders. The company also said it has appointed Patrick Cooke as
acting chief executive officer.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
